name: DailyWorkoutFlashBriefingUS
0:
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Let us devise a varied daily workout for you in your flash briefing. Each day you will get a different set of exercises. You will not get bored and you won't have to plan your workouts in advance. We do it for you.

Always check with your medical professional before starting and new excercise regime.

If you want more information, or a look at older workouts click on the read more link in your Alexa app.

Please leave a review if you like this skill, if you love it why not pop along to our Patreon page and become a supporter.

If you have any suggestions for the skill drop us an email at alexa@two7four.com

Thanks!
